%global __requires_exclude %{?__requires_exclude:%{__requires_exclude}|}^perl\\((POE|POE::Filter::Transparent::SMTP)\\)$

%description
POE::Component::Client::SMTP allows you to send email messages 
in an asynchronous manner, using POE.

